[h2 id=Portal-ForCommodore64??? 
	"Portal - For Commodore 64???
	$LF
]h2
[div class=p 
	"This Portal port (while not a very portal populated Portal port) is an unofficial fan-made Portal port in tribute to the more portal-populated popular Portal port known as, well, 
	[b 
		"Portal.
	]b
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The game can be legally acquired free from 
	[a class=extlink href=https://www.jamiefuller.com/portal/ rel=nofollow 
		"the author's website
	]a
	" in either NTSC or PAL format.  This run uses the NTSC format.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This was released in late 2018. The earliest reference on a specific date I can find was on Dec 2 when 
	[a class=extlink href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pi3oBvn1vaA rel=nofollow 
		"this video
	]a
	" was uploaded by the game's author.
	$LF
]div
